        appStoreUrl: "https://apps.apple.com/us/app/prismbox-connect/id6744375627",
        appStoreLabel: "View Custom iOS Control App",
        appStoreCaption: "The custom-built iOS companion app used to remotely control the smart clock's lighting, weather location, and settings such as display layout.",
        sections: [
          {
            heading: "Vibrant LED Effects",
            text: ["Has dynamic LED lighting that can be customized through the companion app.", "Users can select custom colors, dual gradients, and different animated effects."],
            image: "/images/clock_purple.jpg",
            imageAlt: "Fully Assembled Smart Clock Displaying Purple LED Effects",
            imageLeft: true,
          },
          {
            heading: "3D Enclosure Design",
            text: ["Designed a custom 3D-printable enclosure using CAD software like Autodesk Fusion 360 to house the custom PCB and dual speakers.", "Engineered the casing to provide optimal acoustics for music playback and a clean display area for the OLED screen."],
            image: "/images/smart_clock_cad.png",
            imageAlt: "3D CAD Design of the Smart Clock Enclosure",
            imageLeft: false,
