          {
            heading: "PCB Layout and Design",
            text: ["Designed, ordered, and assembled a custom Printed Circuit Board (PCB) to handle power distribution, microcontroller interfacing, and LED drivers.", "Ensured precise routing for signal integrity and reliable operation of the clock's components."],
            image: "/images/smart_clock_pcb.png",
            imageAlt: "Custom Printed Circuit Board Layout for Smart Clock",
            imageLeft: true,
