            text: ["Architected the complete electrical schematic integrating an ESP32 microcontroller.", "Planned the circuitry to support real-time weather updates, LED control, and seamless internet connectivity."],
            image: "/images/smart_clock_schematic.png",
            imageAlt: "Electrical Schematic Design for Smart Clock",
            imageLeft: false,
          },
          {
