        description: "A comprehensive native iOS application empowering a local clinic with seamless online appointment scheduling, patient reviews, and streamlined communication.",
        backgroundColor: "linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(63, 185, 80, 0.2), rgba(13, 17, 23, 1))",
        appStoreUrl: "https://apps.apple.com/us/app/commonwealth-fmly-chiropractic/id6446209042",
        appStoreLabel: "View on App Store",
        appStoreCaption: null,
        sections: [
          {
            heading: "Custom User Interface",
            text: ["Designed and developed a fully native iOS application from scratch using Swift and Storyboards.", "Created a custom, user-friendly interface to enhance patient engagement and provide quick access to clinic information, locations, and services."],
            doubleImages: ["/images/chiro_about_top.png", "/images/chiro_about_bottom.png"],
            doubleAlts: ["About Us Interface of the Chiropractic iOS Application", "Clinic Services Interface of the Chiropractic iOS Application"],
            imageLeft: true,
          },
          {
            heading: "Online Scheduling & Engagement",
            text: ["Integrated seamless online appointment scheduling for multiple clinic locations (Elizabethtown and Hodgenville).", "Enabled patients to easily leave reviews and access essential clinic details on the go.", "Successfully launched on the App Store, where it maintains a 5-star rating and is utilized daily by patients."],
            image: "/images/chiro_appointments.png",
            imageAlt: "Online Appointment Scheduling Interface of the Chiropractic iOS Application",
            imageLeft: false,
          },
        ],
      },
    ],
  },
  {
    year: "2024",
    projects: [
      {
        id: "shape-invader",
        title: "Shape Invader",
        platform: "Apple Vision Pro",
        description: "Developed and launched an immersive spatial AR/VR game using RealityKit and SwiftUI. Featured among the first 600 apps globally available on the App Store during the Vision Pro launch.",
        image: "/images/shape_invader_gameplay_ar.png",
        appStoreUrl: "https://apps.apple.com/us/app/shape-invader/id6476964958",
        appStoreLabel: "View on App Store",
        appStoreCaption: null,
        sections: [
          {
            heading: "Spatial AR/VR Gameplay",
            text: ["Designed a spatial computing game specifically for Apple Vision Pro.", "Successfully launched alongside the device's release as one of the first 600 apps available globally on the App Store.", "Developed dynamic 3D gameplay using RealityKit's physics engine for accurate collision detection and interactive particle emitters."],
