            image: "/images/shape_invader_gameplay_vr.png",
            imageAlt: "Shape Invader Virtual Reality Gameplay in Space Environment",
            imageLeft: false,
          },
          {
            heading: "Spatial UI & Game States",
            text: ["Utilized SwiftUI to craft intuitive spatial interfaces that float seamlessly in the user's environment.", "Engineered a dynamic UI system that adapts to various game states (Main Menu, Gameplay, Game Over) and visually aligns with the chosen AR or VR environment."],
            doubleImages: ["/images/shape_invader_menu_ar.png", "/images/shape_invader_gameover_vr.png"],
            doubleAlts: ["Shape Invader Main Menu in Augmented Reality", "Shape Invader Game Over Screen in Virtual Reality"],
            imageLeft: true,
          },
        ],
      },
      {
        id: "airshow",
        title: "Aircraft Show",
        platform: "Apple Vision Pro",
        description: "A spatial computing experience built with SwiftUI and RealityKit, enabling users to visualize and interact with high-fidelity 3D aircraft models in fully immersive environments.",
        image: "/images/airshow_flight.jpg",
        appStoreUrl: "https://apps.apple.com/us/app/aircraft-show/id6477761518",
        appStoreLabel: "View on App Store",
        appStoreCaption: null,
        sections: [
          {
            heading: "Immersive Spatial Computing",
            text: ["Developed a spatial computing application natively for Apple Vision Pro using Swift, SwiftUI, and RealityKit.", "Created intuitive, gaze-based glassmorphism user interfaces for users to access detailed aircraft specifications, toggle environments, and control animations seamlessly in their physical space."],
            image: "/images/airshow_ui.png",
            imageAlt: "Spatial User Interface for Airshow in Augmented Reality",
            imageLeft: true,
