          },
        ],
      },
    ],
  },
  {
    year: "2026",
    projects: [
      {
        id: "smart-aquarium",
        title: "Smart Aquarium",
        platform: "IoT / 3D-Printed",
        description: "An automated aquarium system featuring feeding reminders, precise water quality monitoring, custom LED lighting, and seamless Apple AccessorySetupKit integration.",
        image: "/images/aquarium_glowing.jpg",
        appStoreUrl: null,
        sections: [
          {
            heading: "Custom 3D Enclosure Design",
            text: ["Designed and 3D printed a custom aquarium lid using Autodesk Fusion 360.", "Engineered the structure to house the electronics and sensors safely above the water line while maintaining a sleek aesthetic."],
            doubleImages: ["/images/aquarium_cad_full.png", "/images/aquarium_cad_lid.png"],
            doubleAlts: ["Complete 3D CAD Model of the Smart Aquarium Ecosystem", "Detailed Interior CAD View of the Smart Aquarium Lid"],
            imageLeft: true,
          },
          {
            heading: "Custom PCB Design",
            text: ["Designed a custom printed circuit board (PCB) to seamlessly integrate the ESP32 microcontroller with all peripheral sensors.", "Engineered the board to handle power distribution for the sensors and custom LED lighting."],
            image: "/images/aquarium_pcb.png",
            imageAlt: "Custom Printed Circuit Board Layout for Aquarium Electronics",
            imageLeft: false,
          },
          {
            heading: "Hardware & Sensor Integration",
            text: ["Powered by an ESP32 microcontroller that manages a complex array of peripherals and sensors.", "Integrated water quality monitoring (TDS and temperature), a water level sensor, automated bubbler control, and a motorized feeding mechanism.", "Has custom warning light and manual feeding button to alert user when its been too long since last feeding."],
            image: "/images/aquarium_wiring.jpg",
            imageAlt: "Detailed Wiring and Sensor Integration within the Smart Aquarium",
            imageLeft: true,
          },
          {
            heading: "Custom LED Lighting",
            text: ["Engineered dynamic custom LED lighting that can be personalized directly from the app to create stunning visual effects.", "The lighting system is fully controllable, allowing users to match the ambiance to their environment."],
            image: "/images/aquarium_glowing.jpg",
            imageAlt: "Smart Aquarium Illuminated with Custom Green LED Lighting",
            imageLeft: false,
          },
          {
            heading: "Software & iOS Connectivity",
            text: ["Integrated Apple's AccessorySetupKit for secure, seamless Bluetooth and Wi-Fi pairing directly from an iOS device.", "Created a custom iOS companion app using SwiftUI to control the aquarium, schedule automated feeding times, and monitor water parameters in real-time."],
            doubleImages: ["/images/aquarium_app_finding.png", "/images/aquarium_app_dashboard.png"],
            doubleAlts: ["iOS Device Pairing with Smart Aquarium via Apple AccessorySetupKit", "Companion iOS Application Dashboard Built with SwiftUI"],
            imageLeft: true,
          },
        ],
      },
    ],
